87-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAXO4gyWYBvnGNZanTy63UWAXjtbckB4S74QTRkGQ3oJh&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FZwilling-Enfingy-Electric-Kettle-Cordless%2Fdp%2FB085XLXV24%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">双立人的电热水壶</a>烧水<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/zwillings-cool-touch-kettle-irl-153513688.html">速度快得惊人</a>，而且没有外露的加热元件，而某些住房法规不允许这样做。它看起来也很可爱，在我们的实验中，它在两分钟内煮沸了 16 盎司的水。当然，它可以帮助你泡茶或咖啡，但真正的专业级举措是储备<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9zP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE3ei0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiM2YzY2I2ZGYtMTZmOS00MmExLThjODYtNWUwZDEzMzQzZDU4In0&amp;signature=AQAAAbOj3b5pf9bX0sgZQTcdFJ6jxWA6xmbnWMFG0yMs2yhF&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fs" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=instant+cup&amp;i=grocery&amp;crid=198NSNQ79MJV9&amp;sprefix=instant+cup%2Cgrocery%2C197" class="rapid-with-clickid">速溶杯装食品，</a>以满足早晨的燕麦片、午夜的杯面以及其间的渴望。 <em>- 作为</em></p><h2>终极耳朵 Wonderboom 3 </h2><p><core-commerce id="45ff89dd8d5d4105b9900e2d9ebd45b9" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>当他们的手机扬声器无法满足需求时， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0Iw